{
 "name": "RPlog_Nar_Shaddaa_Infiltration",
 "title": "Nar Shaddaa Infiltration",
 "summary": "As war and an Imperial blockade erupt over the Smuggler's Moon, Luke Skywalker in Jedi One and the Sullustan pilot Enb'Zik flying the modified blastboat Vigilance with his co-pilot Lalo race through the chaos using the 'Jedi Harmony' technique Luke has taught him. Threading between bulk freighters and outrunning a half-dozen Ugly fighters, the two ships dive into the moon's atmosphere and make contact with the smuggler Kaitlin over an encrypted channel arranged by Senator Marx. Kaitlin grants them clearance to the Side Deck's repair pad, where Enb'Zik executes a hair-raising landing and Luke steps out of his X-wing to begin their business on Nar Shaddaa.",
